HEADWORD: Stellify
<hw>Stel"li*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>stella</ets> a star + <ets>-fy</ets>.]</ety> <def>To turn into a
star; to cause to appear like a star; to place among the stars, or in
heaven.</def> <mark>[Obs. or R.]</mark> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

